Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:21.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.12,0:21:31.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.82,0:21:37.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是想活还是想死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.62,0:21:39.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想活
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.29,0:21:43.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗  那就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.71,0:21:46.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过就算去了  你的朋友也不在家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.23,0:21:48.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.65,0:21:51.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.75,0:21:54.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我还是想死好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.80,0:21:59.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话你能再拿到一根儿童餐上的旗子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.29,0:22:00.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.44,0:22:02.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  真狡猾
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.23,0:22:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸妈妈想要背着我去商场
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.43,0:22:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狡猾  太狡猾了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.21,0:22:12.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的可以吗  你不会后悔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.91,0:22:15.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要后悔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.58,0:22:20.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告诉你  我很坏的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.89,0:22:25.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.33,0:22:29.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管发生什么事  爸爸妈妈都和我在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.79,0:23:15.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凑足20根了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.57,0:23:21.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天上的神仙  我这样就能幸福了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.86,0:23:24.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美代子  睡觉之前记得要刷牙哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.64,0:23:26.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
